/>\n但係男朋友解釋話對對情侶唔同 有d嗌完散。有d嗌足十幾年 我地係另一種 大家唔鍾意會表達 溝通得好就唔會嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cdd61565de3c4934b79cdbef284879334c9a81","tid":1930652,"uid":50400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T00:14:04.000Z","msg":"嗌交冷戰最on9<br />\n對方唔講嬲咩 解決唔到 2邊都辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861e618a45782b742c71bbbb2383a37feab014b9","tid":1930652,"uid":83411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T00:58:05.000Z","msg":"我同我老婆十幾年，只有開始個年磨合期有嘈過交<br />\n之後未嘈過咁濟"},{"pid":"632c6cff30c6108863263ede27c21aa0fd1396a1","tid":1930652,"uid":118597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T01:05:19.000Z","msg":"拍咗三年幾，好少嘈交，嘈交唔會鬧分手，唔會超過1日唔理對方。<br />\n其實真係要雙方互就，有咩就即刻講，但唔好愈講就愈嬲然後嘈起上嚟。如果當下忍住咗冇講，想再傾翻可以係夜闌人靜互相傾心事個時，個氣氛又ok都可以攤出嚟講。最緊要抱住個心態係想處理好件事唔係想分手。"},{"pid":"7f3d53e766e78155428ab2c6aac1a14aec3982a0","tid":1930652,"uid":61416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d13e7b582c99253d5bc3beb339fb7b78b5e1fee3","tid":1930652,"uid":38440,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T01:11:56.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n拍左3年 一爆已經分手"},{"pid":"16b4eaefc2ff8e7223b1ed725766e356c550bc82","tid":1930652,"uid":82779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T01:13:25.000Z","msg":"我同ex係咁，不過最後都係散左"},{"pid":"803473d17706a22b7535286d0c0c66cc77577b89","tid":1930652,"uid":58353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T01:15:20.000Z","msg":"最憎嘈交<br />\n講真 如果一開始睇岩對方性格<br />\n再嘈交都係無補於事 所以兩個人都有責任"},{"pid":"0f8f4611488f39059bd20ea22861689fc25a036e","tid":1930652,"uid":170616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T02:24:28.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母嘈到就分手 煩到癲"},{"pid":"6dd3327dd33e1f76d5e37ad982dca4db1413a1ed","tid":1930652,"uid":166245,"like":0